snippet: The two presumed Hezbollah members are believed to be behind a deadly bombing of a bus full of Israeli tourists in Bulgaria.
abstract: Two presumed Hezbollah members are believed to be behind deadly bombing of bus full of Israeli tourists in Bulgaria.

byline.original: By MATTHEW BRUNWASSER and NICHOLAS KULISH
byline.contributor: Hwaida Saad contributed reporting from Beirut, Steven Erlanger from Paris, and Ian Austen from Ottawa.

lead_paragraph: The two presumed Hezbollah members are believed to be behind a deadly bombing of a bus full of Israeli tourists in Bulgaria.
